name: Terrior - Nordic Initials - Vest
description:
Blue spray effect custom cut vests with TBSA in Anglo Saxon. Nice!
As with all our screen printed shirts we recommend a cool hand wash.
Because of the dying process exact patterns and colours may vary. Small printing anomalies may occur.
100% cotton

   Preshrunk Jersey knit
 	-	Deluxe 30's Soft style yarns
 	-	Seamless double needle 7/8 collar
 	-	Double needle hem
 	-	Rolled forward shoulders for better fit
 	-	Double needle sleeve and bottom hems
 	-	Quarter-turned to eliminate center crease

Sizes small, medium, large and extra large

Please allow up to 21 days for delivery
